title: Easy, Everyday Foundation Tutorial
description:
A quick and easy tutorial on one of my FAVORITE foundation combos!!  This is how I do my makeup for school, daytime, and occasionally for going out.

Products Mentioned:
Laura Mercier Tinted Moisturizer SPF 20 in "Sand"
Too Faced Amazing Face Flexible Foundation SPF 15 in "Honey Beige"
Sephora Multi-Purpose Sponge

Visit My Blog:
http://www.tortsandatiara.com
